.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"aX","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"A Files Storage System handles upload, storage, and retrieval\nof arbitrary files — from tiny docs to multi-GB videos. The\nplatform covers chunked upload, metadata indexing, versioning,\nand CDN-backed delivery for consumers and automation pipelines.","height":80,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#E2E4ED","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1488910583,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":72,"angle":0,"y":-3580.9119973887227,"width":505.903564453125},{"seed":1731929497,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"UfSgZ8HCisgnfTajKOO9N","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772978201421,"locked":false,"text":"Why It Is Hard","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"aY","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Why It Is Hard","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#E2E4ED","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1367504377,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":72,"angle":0,"y":-3482.9119973887227,"width":133.82992553710938},{"seed":2144668281,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"jTFMV-hwKsUDiadku4Jd2","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772978201421,"locked":false,"text":"Three distinct problems hide under a simple interface. Chunking\nsplits multi-GB uploads into ~5MB pieces and reassembles them\nafter partial failures. Metadata lookup resolves path hierarchies\nacross billions of files in under 10ms. Sync keeps all clients\nconsistent with conflict detection and no silent data loss.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"aZ","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Three distinct problems hide under a simple interface. Chunking\nsplits multi-GB uploads into ~5MB pieces and reassembles them\nafter partial failures. Metadata lookup resolves path hierarchies\nacross billions of files in under 10ms. Sync keeps all clients\nconsistent with conflict detection and no silent data loss.","height":100,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#E2E4ED","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1451409943,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":72,"angle":0,"y":-3454.9119973887227,"width":502.19149780273438},{"seed":966742873,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"dRmF3K02pBan5rF37Z1T-","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772978201421,"locked":false,"text":"Key Challenges","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"aa","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Key Challenges","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#E2E4ED","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1502826201,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":72,"angle":0,"y":-3334.9119973887227,"width":125.2799072265625},{"seed":1491959865,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"2xeym7itfYMt_TYHM8yXX","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772978201421,"locked":false,"text":"Content-addressing deduplicates storage but complicates deletion\nvia reference counting. Concurrent edits must surface as conflict\ncopies, not silent overwrites. Multi-region replication for\n99.99% SLA introduces lag in read-your-own-writes guarantees.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"ab","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Content-addressing deduplicates storage but complicates deletion\nvia reference counting. Concurrent edits must surface as conflict\ncopies, not silent overwrites. M